<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Hello <%= user || "name" %>
    </h1>
    <p>
        A new reply has been added to your question in the video "<%= title || "Untitled" %>".
    </p>
    <p>
        Please log in to our website to view the reply and continue the
        discussion.
    </p>
    <p>Thank you for being part of our community!</p>
</body>

</html>